comments: Harris (PHI) establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Mitchell (CLE) legally contests Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) briefly places his arm on Mobley's (CLE) arm as both players pursue the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Bamba (PHI) wraps Mobley (CLE) around his opposite-side hip.
Garland (CLE) legally contests Lowry's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) makes hand on ball contact and cleanly deflects the ball away from Garland (CLE).
Mobley (CLE) moves alongside Maxey's (PHI) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Bamba (PHI) legally contests Mobley's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Lowry (PHI) establishes himself in Allen's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.  The two players mutually engage after the contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) reaches in and initiates contact to Bamba's (PHI) arm which affects his play at the basket.
Lowry (PHI) initiates contact with Niang's (CLE) arm and affects his SQBR.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) initiates contact with Mitchell's (CLE) arm during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Strus (CLE) contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
